HEADWORD: Penner
<hw>Pen"ner</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
pens; a writer.</def> <rj><au>Sir T. North.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A case for holding pens.</def>
